    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and it still has that fresh, like-new feel! It drives like a cloud and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that's been loved and meticulously cared for, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for it to go to a great home, so come by and take a look!",
