    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S, a masterclass in the 997.1 silhouette. This example is powered by a mid-mounted 3.8L flat-six engine, producing a linear 355 hp with an uncompromising redline. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, featuring short-throw shifts and a perfectly weighted clutch take-up. The chassis is bolstered by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), maintaining optimal geometry and damping under high lateral G-loads. The braking system utilizes four-piston aluminum monoblock calipers clamped over vented, cross-drilled rotors, showing no signs of fade or glazing. Every component, from the hydraulic steering rack to the dry-sump lubrication system, has been maintained to an exacting standard, ensuring the communicative feedback and mechanical harmony expected of a flagship Zuffenhausen product.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
