    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a benchmark for the 'mint' standard. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that retains its original deep-gloss luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirls, or scratches. The interior is equally breathtaking; the premium leather remains supple and matte, free from any bolster wear or UV fading, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is flawless. It comes with a complete, chronologically organized service history performed exclusively by certified technicians using OEM parts. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its history of fair-weather use only. With no modifications, no prior accidents, and a smoke-free history, this is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a showroom-quality example that performs exactly as it did the day it was delivered.",
      "price": 48500.0,
